item.title: What happened to Kanye?
item.description: Akilah Hughes joins the pod to discuss whether Kanye West has always been a mirror to the American zeitgeist, and what's wrong with all of us. Feed: https://rss.art19.com/panic-world

item.title: The Reaction: Liverpool lift the Premier League Trophy
item.description:
It's the day we've been waiting for - title number 20 has arrived. Join us pitchside at Anfield as we enjoy the magic moment. Mark Benstead is with Robbie Fowler, Phil Thompson, Jay Spearing and Jason McAteer. We also hear from Arne Slot, Virgil van Dijk, Alexis Mac Allister, Ryan Gravenberch, Curtis Jones, Harvey Elliott and a whole host of special guests.Â
